@KaHouIeong - It can happen in different ways; 
Scenario 1 - The calls to multiple APIs are orchestrated by API Gateway (may not be ideal scenario) and the final response is transformed into client specific format.
Scenario 2 - A single call from the APIGateway to Composite Service API that orchestrates calls to diff APIs and responds back to APIGateway where the final response is transformed into client specific format.

